window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>An essential companion to the Third Heaven novels </p> <p>At the end of <i>The Third Heaven Apocalypse of Kings</i>, Henel James was invited to discover more about the journalistic Grigori. </p> <p>Why has the reporter been summoned to Heaven? What would Argoth the Prince of House Grigori want? </p> <p>This original story from Donovan M. Neal expands on earlier events that helped shape the angelic-world of the Third Heaven Universe, with some surprising nods to the Third Heaven stories that will delight fans of the books. </p> <p>Return to the realm of angels, to the time before time: a time before the rise of fallen stars, and explore the realm of Limbo...the realm where all your choices live and from which no one can escape. </p> <p>Listen to the first book of this exciting new series now.</p>"; 
